### Variables
@BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080
@BASE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### Endpoints

#### Health Check
GET {{BASE_URL}}/health

#### Create VM
POST {{BASE_API_URL}}/vms
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "vm-01",
    "cpu": 1,
    "memory": 512,
    "disk_size": 4,
    "image": "ubuntu-24.04"
}

#### List VMs
GET {{BASE_API_URL}}/vms


#### Get VM Details
GET {{BASE_API_URL}}/vms/2d871979-4d75-4c1e-ae5c-18319cfd231d


#### Start VM
# POST {{BASE_API_URL}}/vms/{id}/start
POST {{BASE_API_URL}}/vms/2d871979-4d75-4c1e-ae5c-18319cfd231d/start


#### Stop VM
POST {{BASE_API_URL}}/vms/2d871979-4d75-4c1e-ae5c-18319cfd231d/stop


#### Delete VM
DELETE {{BASE_API_URL}}/vms/2d871979-4d75-4c1e-ae5c-18319cfd231d

